<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
  <%- include('./partials/head.ejs') %>
  <body>
    <%- include('./partials/banner.ejs') %>
    <div class="container">
      <%- include('./partials/navbar.ejs') %>
      
      <form id="contact">
        <label for="cName">Name:</label>
        <input type="text" id="cName" name="cName" required> <br/>
        <label for="cEmail">Email:</label>
        <input type="email" id="cEmail" name="cEmail" required><br/>
        <p>Which package is your query about?</p> <br/>
        <input type="radio" id="ans1" name="answers" value="Standard">
        <label for="ans1">Standard</label><br/>
        <input type="radio" id="ans2" name="answers" value="Chosen">
        <label for="ans2">The Chosen One Package</label> <br/>
        <p>We may respond via an owl, on a scale of 1-10, how scared are you of owls?</p><br/>
        <p>(10 is the most scared)</p><br/>
        <input type="number" id="numOwl" name="numOwl" required><br/>
        <label for="query">Please enter your query:</label><br/>
        <input type="textarea" id="query" name="query" required><br/>
        <input type="submit" id="subBtn" name="subBtn" value="Submit">
      </form>

      <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>
    </div>
    <script src="scripts/contact.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
